{"tid":1455654,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果機場走唔哂","createTime":"2019-08-12T09:13:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T09:20:11.000Z","uid":46603,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"539c11edd79189d960befe01c553d5af8b150c68","tid":1455654,"uid":46603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:13:51.000Z","msg":"就算所有人有共識要走<br />\n1-2個鐘內應該車唔走哂所有人 <br />\n如果真係要揀 你地覺得係走得幾多得幾多<br />\n淨番果d 人會愈危險 定係想搏一搏全部人守住機場？ 如果真係守 就要快d 準備 <br />\n現場有咩牌拎得起做防線要拎 整好防線 <br />\n仲有揸車黎既？ 真係去到最後無得走就要團結 <br />\n盡量場地有咩用得著要拎 我地係保護自己 保護機場 <br />\n最難搞係tg"},{"pid":"8e4ae35f3bd2fb86d3223373d5c4cdbf627b87a1","tid":1455654,"uid":159045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:15:09.000Z","msg":"真係咩都唔好理 有巴士有的士~ 就快上"},{"pid":"a47ec727dc3819ce1c61612778ab98865065a74c","tid":1455654,"uid":186845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:17:50.000Z","msg":"走呀 目標已達！！趁有車好走啦！！陣間冇車走唔到就送頭啦！！咁多人一齊好難走到！！"},{"pid":"6b129770da5b84360918f22114fa69d99f4b8253","tid":1455654,"uid":186845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:18:48.000Z","msg":"有咩巴士就上咩巴士"},{"pid":"f9e827fa714fa9c1d2a0233adf30a07f36a1cbd5","tid":1455654,"uid":77803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:20:11.000Z","msg":"必要時向港珠澳去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}